# LLM SEO (AEO)

When editing matching pages, read and follow:

- `.cursor/skills/llm-seo/SKILL.md`
- `.cursor/skills/llm-seo/reference.md`
- `.cursor/skills/write-docs/SKILL.md` for leads, GitBook, and SUMMARY

## Required habits

- Answer-first lead (2–3 sentences)
- Stable category phrase once when defining the product
- Support labels: Native / Certified / Compatible with caveats / Hosted / Roadmap / Experimental
- Facts as tables or lists; 3+ internal links
- No competitor trademarks; roadmap engines not installable
- Unique answer-first frontmatter description

## Database pages

Lead → support label → connection → features matrix → limitations → MCP link → Related.
